OL,7,GThe BBC's director of nations says he
OL,8,Gdoesn't think the BBC is trying to take
OL,9,Gthe 'Local' out of Local Radio as
OL,10,Gproposed changes to the network of
OL,11,Gstations in England continue to face
OL,12,Gstrong criticism.
OL,14,FSpeaking to BBC Radio Derby's Ian Skye,
OL,15,FRhodri Talfan Davies admitted he had
OL,16,Freceived "hundreds and hundreds of
OL,17,Fletters" since the proposals were first
OL,18,Fannounced. He was criticised on-air for
OL,19,Ffailing to consult audiences and staff.
