PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F352A1669042615
OL,7,FThe BBC plans to cut back local radio
OL,8,Fprogrammes to run between 6am and 2pm
OL,9,Fon weekdays. During the remaining
OL,10,Fhours, local stations would carry a
OL,11,Frange of national, regional and
OL,12,Fsub-regional programmes, except when
OL,13,Flocal stations broadcast live sport.
OL,15,FThe BBC says the changes are needed in
OL,16,Forder to reallocate resources to online
OL,17,Fservices and local podcasts.
