OL,7,FDavies admitted he'd received letters
OL,8,Fexpressing concern over plans for
OL,9,Fweekends and sharing programmes across
OL,10,Fcounty boundaries.
OL,12,FHe told Ian Skye the BBC was listening
OL,13,Fto concerns from MPs, stakeholders,
OL,14,Flocal authorities and audiences,
OL,15,Femphasising the plans were still just
OL,16,Fproposals.
