OL,7,FAn urgent question was raised in the
OL,8,FHouse of Commons last week when culture
OL,9,Fminister Julia Lopez confirmed the DCMS
OL,10,Fhadn't been briefed on the plans prior
OL,11,Fto publication. The minister confirmed
OL,12,Fshe would be meeting BBC bosses.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, proposals to merge the BBC
OL,15,FNews Channel with its international
OL,16,Fcounterpart continue with less
OL,17,Fbacklash.
