OL,7,FThe channel launched 25 years ago today
OL,8,Fas BBC News 24. Unlike 5 years ago, the
OL,9,Foccasion was not marked by the BBC on a
OL,10,Fday dominated by rolling news coverage
OL,11,Fof the US midterms simulcast with BBC
OL,12,FWorld News.
OL,14,FAhead of April's changes, UK-specific
OL,15,Foutput on the channel continues to
OL,16,Fdwindle. Last month saw the long
OL,17,Frunning Film Review segment come to an
OL,18,Fend.
